paragraphs.title: List customers that have given consent for marketing who are located in France
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
select * from consent_master.consent_data_trans where marketingconsent='YES' and country='FR'

paragraphs.title: How many EU ww_customer records in total? (etl_user can see full set of EU records - regardless of consent)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
SELECT count(*) FROM hortoniabank.ww_customers_trans

paragraphs.title: How many ww_customer records have given consent and consent hasn't expired? (ivanna_eu_hr can only see this set of EU records)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive_interactive)
SELECT count(*) FROM  hortoniabank.ww_customers where 
    country in (select countrycode from hortoniabank.eu_countries) and 
    insuranceid in (select insuranceid from consent_master.consent_data_trans  where (marketingconsent = 'YES' and current_date < date_add(marketingconsentstartdate, 365)))
